Articles.Content: Because I will only be able to get the new update tomorrow, what are the new parts?

Well, there is the obvious Kerbal seat, and a lot of parts from KSPX. There is the one man lander can, the one man docking pod thing, two unmanned pods, a new engine that is weaker than the Mainsail and stronger than the Poodle, and a new rover wheel. That's all I can remember.
There is also a large docking part.
Larger docking port, don't forget that. It's my favorite.
Now I want to get it more
